<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <title>Email Template</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #E1E4E6; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <!-- Wrapper Table -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
        style="background-color: #E1E4E6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                <!-- Email Container -->
                <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                    style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 100%; ">

                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style=" padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
                                alt="Header Image"
                                style="width: 100%; max-width: 200px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
                        </td>

                    </tr>
                    <tr>

                        <td align="center" style="    background-color: #f8f9fa;
                        color: #006E7D;
                        padding: 20px;
                        text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5;">Welcome to
                                Our Service</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Body -->
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333; text-align: left;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">Dear [Recipient's Name],</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">Thank you for joining us! We are excited to have you on board.
                                Please let us know if you have any questions or need assistance.</p>

                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333; text-align: left;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;"><strong>Name:</strong> Srirajkumar Patcheappane</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;"><strong>Email:</strong> sriraj2694@gmail.com</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;"><strong>Phone:</strong> +9715 63405452</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333; text-align: left;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">Best regards,</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">The CBD Team</p>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333; text-align: left;border-top: 1px solid; ">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">This e-mail was sent from a contact us page on cbd.ae
                                (https://cbd.ae)</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">This message and any files sent with it are confidential. It
                                may not be disclosed to, or used by anyone other than the addressee(s) without the
                                express consent of the sender. If you receive this message in error, please advise the
                                sender immediately.</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center"
                            style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">
                            <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
                                alt="Footer Image"
                                style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">

                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>

</html>
